## ğŸ“¡ Overview

**Nmap (Network Mapper)** is a powerful network reconnaissance tool used to:

- Discover live hosts
- Identify open ports
- Detect running services
- Check software versions
- Fingerprint operating systems
- Analyze firewall behavior

> **No scan = no awareness.** Nmap turns the unknown into the known.

